data: Listen up, Perverts! If you want to taste the real hardcore, enter the dungeon!
To be expected - he was the very best. Are you ready - in case?
Responding to intercepted call. ... Daniel Lamb, this is your last chance. Give yourself up!
Are you crazy? He's an animal and Danny barely remembers who I am!
Slippery bastard. Fuck it, we got him holed up in there. Where's he gonna go?
If he sees you, he will kill you. Understand? WASTE HIM!
Don't dare speak that name to me! I am in control, and we will prevail!
Remember - 'alive' if you can manage it. If not, get the head to me as soon as possible.
I know it's difficult, Danny, but you must go back to that night. I need you to remember.
You two light up and cover this area. The chopper'll do a circle sweep of the shadows.
My God...Danny? Is that you? What are you doing here?
The streets will be crawling with Bloodhounds - we need to find another way out of here.
Pickman is the head scientist for the entire Project. We need him - alive.
We need a weapon. Get a syringe from the supplies office.
Safe house... All these clippings, photos of me... I put these here... to make me remember.
She knows more than she's saying. I've got to talk to her again.
Aww, fuck it, Pickman only wants the head. Send the chopper over to soften him up.
I remember this place. The person I'm looking for is here somewhere.
Wait, that's not right - Leo and I talk all the time...
You expect me to lay down and die?
They've seen us - you're gonna have to deal with those orderlies before you get in the truck.
You heard the APB, people. That serial killer from the Plaza is headed for our happy little community.
If I speak the failsafe phrase, your brain will be wiped clean! Do you really want that?
That's it Danny. Listen to me and I'll get us out of here.
It`s just the usual BS. There`s gonna be a fire drill on Friday too.
Cletus, when I give the word I want you to flush that sucker out.
I see that bastard! He's right there!
Well, we need to find a way inside.
Not here. Let's try upstairs in the bedrooms.
There`s just one more person to take care of. After that - freedom.
You did good, Danny. Now go find some first aid, patch yourself up.
This guy stands between you and freedom.
Good, I`ll bolt the animal lab from the inside.
This is not you, you don't have to do this.
Show no mercy, Danny. This whole town is a Project dormitory.
Here he comes! Fall back to the house!
This is the place. You left a drug in there that'll clear your head.
That bastard slipped right through! But he ain't gettin' far.
We don't want to be disturbed.
You still got it - they didn't see a thing.
Grimmins? Venchek? Where are they? I`ve had enough of these amateurs.
Are you cold? Come inside. I'll warm you up.
But he`s a nurse - he`ll help me.
This is our last chance, Watchdogs. Take up your positions and ready your weapons.
Here are some more of your victims to chew on!
You want to get out of here?
I'm not gonna let you kill me.
We got him corralled, boys. Go get him!
Spengler - look for Higgs and Spaulding - they're coming up from the adult speciality shop.
You can`t leave those bodies in full view...
Shit - what are we going to do?
Get rid of all those Watchdogs.
Guys come in expecting a blowjob, they go out Project zombies.
This wasn't supposed to happen, Danny! The bridge in your head is malfunctioning!
I`ll scout ahead Danny. Get your head straight and follow me.
Danny, it's locked, we need to find another way to get to him.
You`re not telling me the whole story Leo.
Georgy-boy! C'mon in! Jeez, you look like shit.
Nice one, Danny. Follow the drain but try and find a way back onto the street.
Go to the safe house and wait for me there.
Hide the bodies in the shadows
If that guy lives, we're dead.
Alright, after the third sweep, he`s all yours.
Hey, buddy. Don't go snoopin', alright?
Where can you run to now, huh? You're cornered like a sick dog.
Sweep this place. Start at the basement. I`ll search the bedrooms.
Nah, they`re just checking we know how to use the intruder lockdown system. Easy as cake.
Do? We`re gonna do what they trained us to do. We`re gonna kill them.
Isn't Dr Whyte down in the psycho section?
Go on, try it. See how it feels to own a life.
Shit! Another Watchdog... Take him out!
Why don`t you stay where I can see ya, tough guy?
B team is coming in from the harbour - let's show him what we do to Project traitors.
They're not going to hear us with this music blasting.
Hide in the shadows. These guys are vicious, remember?
I don`t want to hurt anybody!
Look at this... a massacre. What happened?
More deliveries? Man, it`s been non-stop all week.
You have to take this psycho down, Danny!
I tell you the whole story and your brain would implode. Trust me.
Search all the cabinets and trunks.
I've got some unfinished business here, Danny. Something I need to do alone.
Just got a call from head office...
Fuck! You stay there. Let's see how this guy fares in the open.
That psycho's in the shop! HELP! HELP!
Don't let these crazies spot you.
They`d rip your head off in a heartbeat.
There's a guy here asking for Judy...
Nice. Now all we need is a syringe. Try the bathroom.
He`s trying to get to the train yard.
Two minds in one body, unaware of each other...
This is our fucking turf now, the Kings are taking over!
The results have been the same since Dr. La-

Holy fuck - that ain`t supposed to happen.
Who cares? They were all working for the Project.
Michael said they'd messed with my head.
I want you looking in every garbage can, mailbox, and goddamn treehouse for this guy.
Those pliers can cut a hole in the wire mesh.
Pickman thought his mercenaries could destroy Leo. I believe the only person who can stop him is you.
Move into the shadow - they can't see you in the darkness.
You keep watch on this one. Anyone comes through this door who ain`t us - waste him.
This must be the safe house. What a shithole.
I don`t know your face and only faces I know get in. Get the fuck outta here.
How about a visit from some old friends? You remember what you did to these guys... don't you?
10 minutes? No problem sir, we'll keep him entertained...
Er, can you wait a minute, I'll check...to see.
Find a way out of the building

Can I have a word, Sergeant?
Two squads of our finest agents are waiting to say hello.
What seest thou else in the dark backward and abysm of time...
Shut up. This guy ain't dangerous, especially unarmed. He shows up and you're first to die.
Smash the light so we can hide.
Fuck the Project! I quit, I quit!
Snap out of it, it's me, Michael! Remember?

Find a way to the train yard

I know, you fool! I invented it! But these results are not nearly good enough. Shut it down.

TV MK? I watch that channel all the time.
I don't know how he found me.
Don't threaten me, Pickman. I won't do this anymore! I quit!
Meet up with Leo at the train yard
Subject A is far too dominant. If we take the bridge out now, the latent personality will be lost forever.
Exactly, come on, let's deal with Pickman.
